Name: Jgsw
About the game: Jigsaw puzzles - the time-tested solution to an excess of free time. Jgsw is a game where you build jigsaw puzzles, either on your own or online with friends. Choose from a variety of included artworks, or even upload your own! Jgsw's simple controls and interface will let you jump into the challenge right away. Features Play solo or online with friends Customizable artwork is as simple as pasting a link Huge puzzles with 5000+ pieces for those seeking a challenge Unique and varied edge shapes keep the puzzles from getting stale Convenient sorting piles let you quickly organize pieces by color or shape or however you like 3D puzzle pieces for a more immersive feel
